    {
      "bookmarkId": "844674_5_1561-1630",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "1561-1630",
      "markText": "他对同盟会“十六字”纲领中“驱除鞑虏”，有不同的看法，认为把满族称为“异族”不妥，这只不过是满汉两民族之间的矛盾罢了，为何要加以“驱除”？",
      "totalCount": 105,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=844674&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1561&rangeEnd=1630",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee3320d05ce382ee34e4021?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=1561&rangeEnd=1630"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "844674_12_13798-13848",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "13798-13848",
      "markText": "在30年代初期，全国各个红色根据地都存在不同程度的肃反。赣西南苏区肃清AB团时，屠杀7万多红军官兵。",
      "totalCount": 102,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=844674&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=13798&rangeEnd=13848",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee3320d05ce382ee34e4021?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=13798&rangeEnd=13848"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "844674_6_10969-10999",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "10969-10999",
      "markText": "陈独秀不参加会议就是对马林包办大会的强烈抵制，这是根本原因。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=844674&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10969&rangeEnd=10999",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee3320d05ce382ee34e4021?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=10969&rangeEnd=10999"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "844674_6_12714-12745",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "12714-12745",
      "markText": "斯大林与共产国际之所以这样做，其目的是服从于苏俄利益的需要的。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=844674&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=12714&rangeEnd=12745",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee3320d05ce382ee34e4021?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=12714&rangeEnd=12745"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "844674_12_6962-7014",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "6962-7014",
      "markText": "在革命时期的权力场上，没有人不是经过斗争而上台的，这是一条亘古不变的真理，也是夺取和执掌权力的不二法门。",
      "totalCount": 90,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=844674&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=6962&rangeEnd=7014",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee3320d05ce382ee34e4021?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=6962&rangeEnd=7014"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "844674_7_10995-11064",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "10995-11064",
      "markText": "就这样，身患重病、手无缚鸡之力，又戴着重度近视眼镜、根本无法掩饰其身份的瞿秋白留在被敌人重重包围的中央苏区，随着其他留下的同志一道打游击。",
      "totalCount": 80,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=844674&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10995&rangeEnd=11064",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee3320d05ce382ee34e4021?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=10995&rangeEnd=11064"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "844674_6_17438-17535",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "17438-17535",
      "markText": "鲁迅1934年8月1日写《忆刘半农君》说到陈独秀：“假若将韬略比作一间仓库罢，独秀先生的是外面竖一面大旗，大书道：内皆武器，来者小心！但那门却开着的，里面有几支枪，几把刀，一目了然，用不着提防。",
      "totalCount": 75,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=844674&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=17438&rangeEnd=17535",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee3320d05ce382ee34e4021?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=17438&rangeEnd=17535"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "844674_6_11425-11511",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "11425-11511",
      "markText": "，陈独秀把桌子一拍说：“各国革命有各国情况，我们中国是个生产事业落后的国家，我们要保留独立自主的权力，要有独立自主的做法，我们有多大的能力干多大的事，决不让任何人牵着鼻子走",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=844674&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=11425&rangeEnd=11511",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee3320d05ce382ee34e4021?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=11425&rangeEnd=11511"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "844674_9_9949-10022",
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "range": "9949-10022",
      "markText": "为了纪念他们的结合，瞿秋白在一枚金别针上亲自刻上“赠我生命的伴侣”七个字，送给杨之华。这一爱情的信物，后来一直伴随着杨之华度过了风风雨雨的几十年。",
      "totalCount": 70,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=844674&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=9949&rangeEnd=10022",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee3320d05ce382ee34e4021?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=9949&rangeEnd=10022"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "844674_4_2902-2943",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2902-2943",
      "markText": "他学识渊博，工宋诗，写隶书，对旧学很有根底，还懂日、英、法三国文字，新学造诣尤深。",
      "totalCount": 68,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=844674&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2902&rangeEnd=2943",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/ee3320d05ce382ee34e4021?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2902&rangeEnd=2943"
    },
